I have only to add, that I wiſh you an untarniſhed Bliſs in the Company of your poliſhed Friend, and that you may enjoy each
other's Friendſhip even to the Age of old NESTOR,
Whoſe Tongue dropp'd Honey; full of Days was he;
Two Ages paſt, he liv'd the Third to ſee;
And, his firſt Race of Subjects long decay'd,
O'er their Sons' Sons a peacefull Scepter ſway'd. POPE's Homer.

Yeſterday, I had the Company of Miſs LEA, and Mr. HILTON, a very
modeſt and ingenious Man, who came with Lord DUDLEY from London;
beſides two other Parties of Viſitants, who engroſſed my whole Day.

BEING gone for a few Days to Hampton-Court, I did not
receive the Favour of yours ſo ſoon as you might naturally imagine,
conſequently it was not in my Power to write to you by the returning Poſt;
and ever ſince being full of Employment, I deferred that Pleaſure till the
preſent Moment, which I fear will produce little worth your Attention;
however, ſuch as it is I give unto you.
